cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "geo-data-discovery: verified FAIR data discovery and dark-data forensics for the geosciences"
abstract: >-
  A two-mode tool that finds directly-downloadable Earth, marine, atmospheric and
  solid-Earth science data with machine-verified access links and schema.org / DCAT
  metadata, and runs a forensic trail (academic provenance, data steward, proxy
  datasets) when data is not in standard infrastructures. Enforces a verification
  gate that prevents hallucinated download links. Distributed as a Claude Skill and
  a standalone Python engine.
type: software
